CLick on the hack you want to use.
Press Ctrl + A. This selects all of the code.
Press Ctrl + C. THis copies all of the code.
At the top right of the page, where the url is click the star.
In the name box write what you want to call the hack.
Click more.
Triple click the url box to select the url.
Press Backspace.
Press Ctrl + V. This pastes the code.
Press save.
To use the hack if the hack doesn't appear below the url press Ctrl + Shift + B.
